		{
			description: [
				"This world is huge — and you don't have to walk all of it."
				""
				"§bWaystones§r let you build a fast-travel network you can access from anywhere in the world."
				""
				"§bTraveler's Backpack§r gives you a wearable storage solution with built-in tanks and crafting access."
				""
				"§bHang Gliders§r, §bAir Balloons§r, and §bImmersive Aircraft§r let you take to the skies in style."
			]
