		{
			dependencies: ["2F2E3D4C5B6A78A1"]
			description: [
				"§bWaystones§r are craftable structures that let you teleport between named locations."
				""
				"Place one down and right-click to name it and add it to your network. You can then warp to it from any other Waystone — or by holding the §eReturn Scroll§r."
				""
				"Craft a §eWaystone§r with chiseled stone bricks, a lodestone, and an ender pearl in the recipe."
			]
			id: "2F2E3D4C5B6A78A2"
			rewards: [{
				count: 1
