		{
			dependencies: ["2F2E3D4C5B6A78A1"]
			description: [
				"§bTraveler's Backpack§r is a wearable backpack with large inventory space and two built-in fluid tanks."
				""
				"Equip it on your back (sneak + right-click) and access it by right-clicking with an empty hand. You can also open it by pressing a bound key."
				""
				"It keeps its inventory when removed — and you can pick up fluid in the tanks with a bucket. Great for long expeditions."
			]
			id: "2F2E3D4C5B6A78A4"
			rewards: [{
				count: 16
