			x: 2.0d
			y: -2.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2F2E3D4C5B6A78A1"]
			description: [
				"The §bHang Glider§r lets you launch from any height and glide long distances without consuming hunger or fuel."
				""
				"Craft it and hold it in your hand. Jump off a high point to deploy — you glide forward while slowly descending."
				""
				"Sneak while gliding to angle downward faster. Look up to slow your descent and extend your flight time."
			]
