		{
			dependencies: ["2F2E3D4C5B6A78A5"]
			description: [
				"§bAir Balloons§r are craftable flying platforms you can ride into the sky."
				""
				"Place a Basket on the ground, attach a Balloon on top, and right-click to board. Use the included controls to ascend, descend, and drift."
				""
				"Balloons move with the wind, so plan your landing approach. They can be dyed any colour and make a surprisingly dignified way to travel."
