			description: [
				"§bImmersive Aircraft§r adds full pilotable vehicles: biplanes, helicopters, and more."
				""
				"Craft a §6Biplane§r for fast horizontal flight. The §6Gyrodyne§r (helicopter) can hover and ascend vertically — perfect for landing anywhere."
				""
				"Aircraft run on fuel — keep §ebuckets of fuel§r on hand. They take damage from crashes, so learn their handling before flying over lava."
